<br>
I for one, do not believe that we are inviting guilds too fast.  Nor do i believe that the SGA is &quot;big enough already&quot;.  I have made a few attempts at leading small raids to various locations.  To date it has been difficult to get as many participants as i would like for the raids i have planned.  Recognizing that this is probably in part due to my inexperience with organizing raids, I would nonetheless probably have benefited from having a larger group of members to draw from.  <br>
<br>
